    public class SeleniumTable
extends SeleniumComponent
implements br.ufmg.dcc.saotome.beholder.ui.table.Table
    The class SeleniumTable implements the Table interface. A table component is a set of cells organized by lines and columns. The objective of this class is making easy the user to recover the information of this cells.
